Introduction

Jeong Sunhye is a South Korean rapper, dancer, singer-songwriter, and composer under BEATS Entertainment and DSP Media. She is best known as the oldest, the leader, and the main rapper of the girl group YOUNG POSSE.

On October 18, 2023, Sunhye officially debuted with YOUNG POSSE with the mini album "MACARONI CHEESE EP". Sunhye came up with the debut title song "Macaroni Cheese" during a composition class after spotting a poster of a macaroni cheeseburger. The image stuck with her throughout the class, inspiring her to start writing about it.
